(258, 1, '2014-08-12 07:04:13', '2014-08-12 07:04:13', 'An influencer can be thought of as someone who can shape the behaviors and purchasing decisions of others. Industries including fitness and allied health are strong relationship businesses and as such are well suited for influencer marketing. In the case of Influence Marketing the goal is to build a mutually beneficial relationship for the business, the influencer and the customer.\r\n\r\nIn the 1970’s there was what is now a famous slogan by the banking firm E.F. Hutton: “When E.F. Hutton talks, people listen”. This is what influencers do, when they talk, people listen.\r\n\r\nYou can think about categorizing Influencers into a four categories based on reach and relevance\r\n\r\nReach: how many target customers listen to the influencer\r\n\r\nRelevance: how close are the interests between what the influencer is saying and those of the target customer.\r\n<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="middle">Low Relevance High Reach</td>\r\n<td valign="middle">High Relevance High Reach</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="middle">Low Relevance Low Reach</td>\r\n<td valign="middle">High Relevance Low Reach</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nLet’s imagine that you have a mobile app that’s targeted only Fitness Professional who are qualified to teach your courses. In order to access the content on the mobile app they need to have attended on of your courses and have been invited to join the app.\r\n\r\nFor a more targeted niche product like this Relevance will be more important than reach.\r\n\r\nWho might be influencers in each of these categories for this product?\r\n\r\nLow Relevance High Reach: Johhny Manziel (pro football quarterback)\r\n\r\nLow Relevance Low Reach:  Friend of Fitness Professional\r\n\r\nHigh Relevance High Reach: Fitness Industry presenter or companies CEO\r\n\r\nHigh Relevance Low Reach: Course Master Trainer\r\n\r\nNow, imagine a Yoga app that is available for anyone to access. Since the app is less targeted than the prior example, Reach will play a more important role, although Relevance still trumps Reach.\r\n\r\nWho might be example influencers in each of these categories for this product?\r\n\r\nLow Relevance High Reach: Justin Bieber\r\n\r\nLow Relevance Low Reach:  Companies accounts payable manager\r\n\r\nHigh Relevance High Reach: Top Yoga Bloggers\r\n\r\nHigh Relevance Low Reach: Master Trainers\r\n\r\nInfluencer marketing involves building and sustaining relationships with the E.F. Hutton’s of your industry. To assist in evaluating your industry influencers you might consider ranking them based on their Klout Score: www.Klout.com\r\n\r\nThe focus on relationships reinforces the focus isn’t about a sale or transaction to the influencer, rather for them to develop and authentic belief in what you offer. Searching for the mutually beneficial opportunities to partner with Influencers and playing the long-game strategy will enable these efforts to return their value multiple times.', 'Influencer Marketing for Sustained Growth', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '252-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-08-12 07:04:13', '2014-08-12 07:04:13', '', 252, 'http://localhost/252-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
